{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a policy of taking the whole group, the girls and the boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you were not separated, because the purpose of us being together was, to go and to-- after the war, to go and to create a settlement.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, so they, they were very careful not to break up the, the unit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all lived in the military barracks with the, with the girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the girls were also in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even myself, that I could not do certain duty in the field, I could drive a jeep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I could do other military tasks and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the War of Independence, the Palmach was disband, because Israel already had a regular military force.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the group as a whole returned back to the kibbutz, except for some special-- some of our guys that became specialists in certain military areas.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They remained sort of almost on loan to the army, because--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I returned back with the most of the group--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to the, to the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And eventually, we, we, we were, we were put together with other groups, because in order to have a settlement, you needed at least the equivalent of 120 people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we made, we made acquaintance and friends with other groups.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think in 1949, the beginning of 1949, the-- our group went to the Negev, in the-- in, in, sort of in the south of Israel, near a city, near Be'er Sheva, south of Be'er Sheva.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we established a settlement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still remained-- I had-- did not conclude yet my school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remained in Kibbutz Yagur till I finished my school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I owed them, sort of, for my sustenance, a certain amount of days.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
